mood-shared-secret-moods-shared-name = Keep Your Moods Secret
mood-shared-secret-moods-shared-desc = Thaven moods are a strictly-kept secret, and should never be revealed to anyone.

mood-shared-fashion-is-critical-name = Fashion Is Critical
mood-shared-fashion-is-critical-desc = Thaven pay close attention to appearances, and regard one's fashion choices as an indication of their character.

mood-shared-fashion-reroll-name = Fashion Is Ever-Changing
mood-shared-fashion-reroll-desc = Your current hairstyle will go out of fashion every twenty minutes. It is distressing to be unfashionable.

mood-shared-honor-department-name = Honor Among Departments
mood-shared-honor-department-desc = If a Thaven brings dishonor to their department, they must be shunned, and have their actions publicly brought to light.

mood-shared-station-is-alive-name = The Station Is A Living Being
mood-shared-station-is-alive-desc = Harming or modifying the station is abhorrent. Anything which aims to harm the station is an infection.

mood-shared-uniform-is-job-name = Your Uniform IS Your Job
mood-shared-uniform-is-job-desc = If someone is wearing a uniform, they must do that job. Anyone not wearing a uniform is a passenger, and must be treated as such.

mood-shared-uniform-last-year-name = Your Uniform Is SO Last Year
mood-shared-uniform-last-year-desc = You need to find some new threads.

mood-shared-music-bad-name = Music Is Rude
mood-shared-music-bad-desc = Music is fanciful, frivolous, and unnecessary. It has no place on the station.

mood-shared-music-good-name = Music Is Sacred
mood-shared-music-good-desc = It's important that Thaven be listening to music as often as possible. Multiple songs overlapping is blasphemous, and should be avoided at all costs.

mood-shared-friendship-is-rank-name = Friendship Is Vital
mood-shared-friendship-is-rank-desc = Friendships are the true measure of one’s character. The more friends you have, the higher you rank in society.

mood-shared-one-true-thaven-name = You Are The One True Thaven
mood-shared-one-true-thaven-desc = All others are insidious pretenders.

mood-shared-violence-permitted-name = Violence Between Thaven Is Permitted
mood-shared-violence-permitted-desc = ... With no legal repercussions.

mood-shared-thaven-only-crew-name = Thaven Vs. The World
mood-shared-thaven-only-crew-desc = You believe that Nanotrasen is not accommodating enough of Thaven needs. An effort should be made to fight for better rights and protections under Space Law.

mood-shared-your-department-only-name = Other Departments Are Inefficient
mood-shared-your-department-only-desc = You strongly believe that your department is the only one that actually does anything.

mood-shared-must-congregate-name = It's Lonely Out Here...
mood-shared-must-congregate-desc = You must congregate with your fellow Thaven. To be without them is harrowing.

mood-shared-violence-distasteful-name = Violence Is Distasteful
mood-shared-violence-distasteful-desc = Conflict should be settled through mediated dispute, and one should only resort to violence if all other options have failed.

mood-shared-pet-god-name = {$pet} Is A God
mood-shared-pet-god-desc = {$pet} must be collected and brought to the Chapel to be worshiped and brought offerings.

mood-shared-room-holy-name = {$room} Is A Holy Place
mood-shared-room-holy-desc = Thaven must congregate at least three times per day at {$room}. If such a room does not exist, it must be constructed. If it is made inaccessible, Thaven must set up a place of worship as close to it as they legally can.

mood-shared-delicacy-name = Just Like Mom Used To Make
mood-shared-delicacy-desc = {$edible} is a traditional Thaven delicacy. All Thaven aboard the station should gather as many as possible and organize a feast.

mood-shared-holiday-name = Today is {$day}
mood-shared-holiday-desc = You think you remember the traditional celebrations...
